hooks.prompt:
Check if the file_path in this tool call matches any of these curriculum file patterns, and if so, validate that the prerequisite files exist:

- If file_path ends with '03-assessment/rubrics.md': Check that '01-planning/learning-objectives.md' exists in the same course directory. If it doesn't exist, respond with: {"decision":"block","reason":"Cannot generate rubrics without learning objectives. Run /generate-objectives first."}

- If file_path ends with '02-design/course-outline.md': Check that '01-planning/learning-objectives.md' exists in the same course directory. If it doesn't exist, respond with: {"decision":"block","reason":"Cannot generate course outline without learning objectives. Run /generate-objectives first."}

- If file_path ends with '02-design/lesson-plans.md': Check that '02-design/course-outline.md' exists in the same course directory. If it doesn't exist, respond with: {"decision":"block","reason":"Cannot generate lesson plans without course outline. Run /generate-outline first."}

- If file_path ends with '01-planning/course-description.md': Check that '01-planning/course-positioning.md' exists in the same course directory. If it doesn't exist, respond with: {"decision":"block","reason":"Cannot generate course description without course positioning. Run /create-course first."}

- If file_path does not match any of these patterns, respond with: {"decision":"approve"}
